{"tid":1044520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電郵生成器廣傳】最後召集！《逃犯條例》、檔案法、資訊自由法 公眾諮詢 就快截止啦","createTime":"2019-03-03T03:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T03:06:35.000Z","uid":138409,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"d037d536b34fa871ad6b3a9bc9106c3ec44a2af5","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"求各位幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未send就send<br />\nclick幾下唔使1分鐘<br />\nsend咗就幫推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前幾個po都無乜聲氣<br />\n雖然公眾諮詢作用唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過盡做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》諮詢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3月4日（明天）截止</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://form.jotform.me/90501893496465?fbclid=IwAR3o6_gtO7mFLvDK9hqeQGeUDvc57ZLNQyqq9OfofkNm9VdS_qXTFD-6t1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fform.jotform.me%2F90501893496465%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3o6_gtO7mFLvDK9hqeQGeUDvc57ZLNQyqq9OfofkNm9VdS_qXTFD-6t1I&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=d3824799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://form.jotform.me/90501893496465?fbclid=IwAR3o6_gtO7mFLvDK9hqeQGeUDvc57ZLNQyqq9OfofkNm9VdS_qXTFD-6t1I</a><br />\n<br />\n法改會檔案法及公開資料諮詢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3月5日截止</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://form.jotform.me/90481537732460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fform.jotform.me%2F90481537732460&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=8800f2fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://form.jotform.me/90481537732460</a>"},{"pid":"af83c13aa22e1247753e4ec6b8effb02d22c49dd","tid":1044520,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b3ab3e37a466cfe7b27811667045c22d06d301c","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:28:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f694703dab8453b43a4be95eed84a0f74f403142","tid":1044520,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":34,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8a634a95c049e3b0c929b87a52a641f93e2e941","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"af83c13aa22e1247753e4ec6b8effb02d22c49dd","tid":1044520,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"點解檔案法 嘅諮詢 咁大件事 連登都無人理㗎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cmtqET\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cmtqET</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">逃犯條例</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/113246_7271807fdfe968236f828c232be40a09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F113246_7271807fdfe968236f828c232be40a09.jpg&h=c681bb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/113248_907b521a4881a561f34f1187581dee4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F113248_907b521a4881a561f34f1187581dee4c.jpg&h=cfef705d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"064390c29a0d3a7cebd0ea3ec57e040c864ed525","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"除咗檔案法之外<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">資訊自由法</span></span>都好緊要㗎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEETKC6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEETKC6.jpg&h=5f22800d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fv7O4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fv7O4Q.jpg&h=1fb8b1cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCWu2pR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCWu2pR.jpg&h=ba61c414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5CVdwy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5CVdwy.jpg&h=739dcd85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港前途研究計畫 有關兩條法例嘅評論<br />\n<br />\n【香港《檔案法》隨時淪為無牙老虎？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1154565504697411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F1154565504697411&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=317dd5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1154565504697411</a><br />\n<br />\n【無獨立專責機構，點要求部門公開重要資訊】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1155134384640523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F1155134384640523&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=b3a64a0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1155134384640523</a><br />\n<br />\n【無資訊自由法？有檔都無得你睇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1155485677938727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F1155485677938727&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=045bc6d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1155485677938727</a><br />\n<br />\n【外國月亮特別圓？&mdash;&mdash;《資訊自由法》在英國的應用及限制】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1187229668097661\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F1187229668097661&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=ef2c9c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1187229668097661</a><br />\n<br />\n【冇檔冇得管，有檔冇得睇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1192263474260947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F1192263474260947&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=2b312e6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1192263474260947</a><br />\n<br />\n【《資訊自由法》諮詢有咩問題？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1184379128382715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F1184379128382715&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=50a5e520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1184379128382715</a>"},{"pid":"be456396ec340820203c5219444310e5fb7f21ab","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點解檔案法緊要</span></span><br />\n// 過去整理英國解密檔案感受很深的是，若然英國沒有訂立《檔案法》，香港人根本沒有機會，透過保存完好的解密檔案中，了解數場框劃香港命運的歷史事件幕後決策過程，以及佐證譚惠珠之流在97前後如何反口覆舌。<br />\n<br />\n沒有英國《檔案法》，這些都會是空白。同樣地，香港沒有一套有牙力、有罰則的《檔案法》，所有有關政改、雨傘運動、魚蛋革命、一連串DQ事件、以至律政司是否檢控689的歷史紀錄，都會是空白。因此，訂立有牙力的《檔案法》，禁止當權者胡亂毀檔，是面對歪理當道世代的重要工具之一。//<br />\n<br />\n// 丁屋一案，正正體現到檔案保存的重要性，如果高官如689咁，可以胡亂銷毀檔案，今日根本沒有任何行政機關的決策討論文件，去證明丁屋政策是否長久措施，結果只會淪為新界佬任意詮釋「傳統權益」的含意，甚至有部分新界人將本來違法的套丁都嘗圖納入「傳統權益」當中。<br />\n<br />\n但再鋒利嘅刀，都有生銹嘅時候。港英沿用的檔案管理制度講求從政者的自律，而主權移交後種種「滅檔」亂象，包括梁振英任內銷毀14億張檔案、橫洲私下摸底無紀錄，已證明過去訴諸自律的制度已到盡頭，有需要推動更有牙力的《檔案法》及《資訊自由法》，才可更有效地監察行政當局的重大決策行為。//"},{"pid":"0b4c8e3c934335103a08b4259ff2d4465bd6c654","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b9681a3b48e8e1a0fc9df9bab23cae9ae946fe3b","tid":1044520,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"泛民冇人做野，港豬自己攞黎"},{"pid":"eab69e0022ad26aaf5641a807aca338175a14266","tid":1044520,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f923a4677184eb0527ebda6286da3c04dd54fcf2","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"eab69e0022ad26aaf5641a807aca338175a14266","tid":1044520,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"而依家條檔案法其實相當廢<br />\n因為佢無訂立罰則<br />\n就算公務員違反都好<br />\n都無乜嚴重後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c300d277d1a1fad0e4391eee553effd564f951","tid":1044520,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbd22316629c5a11d58f437ef90fe3fe91260269","tid":1044520,"uid":141285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:51:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2b7982c4ca1d52ee572f8bb223d6e3b09aeb3680","tid":1044520,"uid":85161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e0c49bba6bb9d1e454deb50fa3d238489a394490","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7c300d277d1a1fad0e4391eee553effd564f951","tid":1044520,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f923a4677184eb0527ebda6286da3c04dd54fcf2","tid":1044520,"uid":138409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"eab69e0022ad26aaf5641a807aca338175a14266","tid":1044520,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"而依家條檔案法其實相當廢<br />\n因為佢無訂立罰則<br />\n就算公務員違反都好<br />\n都無乜嚴重後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"法改會諮詢文件摘要<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkreform.gov.hk/tc/docs/archiveslaw_sc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkreform.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fdocs%2Farchiveslaw_sc.pdf&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=7eb4b0af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkreform.gov.hk/tc/docs/archiveslaw_sc.pdf</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n行政機制 （ 第 1 . 2 至 1 . 5 段 ）<br />\n5 . 現 時 ， 政 府 檔 案 和 歷 史 檔 案 的 管 理 由 行 政 制 度 規 管 ， 在 此 制 度 下 的 中 央 檔 案 管 理 和 服 務 機 關 為 檔 案 處 。 這 個 行 政 制 度 包 含 行 政 署 長 及 檔 案 處 所 公 布 和 更 新 的 多 項 行 政 規 則 、 指 引 和 最 佳 作 業 方 法 。 藉 總 務 通 告 0 9 1 公 布 的 規 定 旨 在 向 政 府 人 員 施 加 強 制 責 任。任 何 政 府 人 員 如 不 遵 從 其 內 所 載 規 定，可 受 到 紀 律 處 分 ， 包 括 口 頭 或 書 面 警 告 、 譴 責 、 嚴 厲 譴 責 、 降 級 、 迫 令 退 休 及 革 職 。<br />\n適用範圍 （ 第 1 . 6 段 ）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">6. 雖 然 各 局 ／ 部 門 須 受 檔 案 管 理 行 政 機 制 規 管 ， 但 公 營 機 構 則 一 般 不受此限。 2 公營機構 ，包括 法 定 組 織 、 接 受 政 府 經 常 撥 款 的 非 政 府 機 構 、 慈 善 及 宗 教 團 體 以 及 私 營 機 構 ， 在 實 質 管 理 及 保存檔案 方 面 ， 均 不 受 政 府 的 檔 案 管 理 行 政 機 制 規 管</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見（來自香港前途研究計畫）<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/16mGrVtsaogCinr2pnsQcDMsRLoHb3PR1/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F16mGrVtsaogCinr2pnsQcDMsRLoHb3PR1%2Fview&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=e30aa507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/16mGrVtsaogCinr2pnsQcDMsRLoHb3PR1/view</a><br />\n<blockquote>諸多事故,如早前的橫洲公屋發展計畫以及公屋屋邨鉛水事件,均顯示現有行政安排未能清晰有效指明決策局 / 部門 (Bureaux/Departments) 的責任,未有要求它們建立並維護完整、準確、易於查閱 並可用的檔案。檔案法應指明建立檔案的法律責任, 並訂明違法的罰則。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a2af4fa55c62eef1e44e420cfd11469d804cbb74","tid":1044520,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"done"},{"pid":"bba4172acfb